# Gantt Task React 19 Korean - Project Structure Guide

## 📁 Project Overview
This is a Korean-localized React Gantt Chart library based on MaTeMaTuK/gantt-task-react with additional features.

## 🗂️ Core Directory Structure

### 📦 Main Entry Points
- [src/index.tsx](mdc:src/index.tsx) - Main library entry point and public API exports
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Package configuration for `gantt-task-react-19-korean`
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Documentation with Korean features

### 🧩 Component Architecture
- `src/components/` - All React components organized by functionality
  - `calendar/` - Date/time header components with Korean locale support
  - `gantt/` - Main Gantt chart container and content
  - `grid/` - Background grid with weekend color support
  - `task-item/` - Individual task rendering (bar, milestone, project)
  - `task-list/` - Left sidebar table with extra columns support
  - `other/` - Utility components (tooltip, scrollbars, arrows)

### 🔧 Core Logic
- [src/types/public-types.ts](mdc:src/types/public-types.ts) - All public interfaces and types
- [src/helpers/date-helper.ts](mdc:src/helpers/date-helper.ts) - Date manipulation with Korean support
- [src/helpers/bar-helper.ts](mdc:src/helpers/bar-helper.ts) - Task bar calculations
- [src/helpers/other-helper.ts](mdc:src/helpers/other-helper.ts) - Utility functions

### 🎨 Styling
- Component-specific CSS modules (`.module.css` files)
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global styles exported with package

### 📝 Example Application
- [example/src/App.tsx](mdc:example/src/App.tsx) - Demo app with all features
- Shows Korean locale usage, extra columns, weekend colors

## 🌟 Key Features Added
1. **Korean Date Expressions** - `locale="kor"` support
2. **Extra Columns** - Customizable table columns with render functions  
3. **Weekend Colors** - Configurable weekend highlighting
4. **Jira-style Today** - Enhanced today indicator

## 🔨 Build System
- Uses `microbundle-crl` for building UMD/ESM bundles
- TypeScript compilation with `.d.ts` generation
- CSS bundling for component styles